class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會俾佢嚇親</blockquote><br />\n之後大聲啲對佢都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 巴打想搵錢私補正好多，補習社少錢而且閑閑地一打六架</blockquote><br />\n其實我純粹係想教下啲𡃁仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 錢唔太少就ok<br />\n我以前冇點補過習 其實收開幾多？</blockquote><br />\n教過2~3年校內功輔/補習班<br />\n去過唔少小學同中學教<br />\n自己覺得教小學生真係要好惡<br />\n唔係佢地根本唔會聽你話<br />\n同埋大部分小學生都係比家長逼去補習<br />\n根本唔會有心機聽你教 只係想你幫佢做功課或練習<br />\n所以教小學生都幾辛苦<br />\n又要管秩序 又要不停做功課<br />\n仲要唔高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你只係想教下𡃁仔/同佢地玩下 建議去教初中補習<br />\n初中大個小小 易教好多<br />\n起碼唔會好似托兒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋會多d學生認真想學野/聽你教<br />\n人工仲高過補小學tim"},{"pid":"6b6e78f7fc2518abb21b7c6aca113731e6309dff","tid":196342,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前係補習社補，試過個小六生瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小六瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n補全科？巴打男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫得巴打就有j㗎啦"},{"pid":"be17341d866d5d2457ddc934db3ee8bad4ca9111","tid":196342,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下至東南亞小學生上至中六都補過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n力威c fu撈埋補習 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54931a862d87528f46b8a942dd2f103d65f336fd","tid":196342,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n可能真係嚇到佢<br />\n臨走時同負責人講完拍拍籮由就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/so